    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Mar 15, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-03-15/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Mar 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-03-15/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Voices In the blogs: Insuring against data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Frictionless tax compliance; ATGs; giving up bonus depreciation and other highlights from our favorite tax bloggers.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.accountingtoday.com/opinion/in-the-blogs-insuring-against-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.accountingtoday.com/opinion/in-the-blogs-insuring-against-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Mobile Working a Major Cause of Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MANCHESTER, UK.  14th March, 2017  Apricorn, the leading manufacturer of software-free, hardware-encrypted USB drives, today announced &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://pressreleases.responsesource.com/news/92800/mobile-working-a-major-cause-of-data-breaches/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://pressreleases.responsesource.com/news/92800/mobile-working-a-major-cause-of-data-breaches/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Report: DOJ to issue indictments on Wednesday against suspects involved in&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;9 to 5 Mac Verizon&amp;rsquo;s acquisition of Yahoo is expected to close during the second quarter of this year. Though, Verizon has said that the data breaches may delay &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://9to5mac.com/2017/03/14/report-doj-to-issue-indictments-on-wednesday-against-suspects-involved-in-yahoo-data-breach/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://9to5mac.com/2017/03/14/report-doj-to-issue-indictments-on-wednesday-against-suspects-involved-in-yahoo-data-breach/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Verizon sought $925 million penalty for Yahoo&amp;rsquo;s lax security&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In a regulatory filing Monday, Yahoo revealed that, in the wake of enormous data breaches, Verizon initially wanted a $925 million discount on its &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.jhnewsandguide.com/jackson_hole_daily/business/verizon-sought-million-penalty-for-yahoo-s-lax-security/article_b9bff6ae-df65-594f-ae0f-00e97b89e0c1.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.jhnewsandguide.com/jackson_hole_daily/business/verizon-sought-million-penalty-for-yahoo-s-lax-security/article_b9bff6ae-df65-594f-ae0f-00e97b89e0c1.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;You may soon have the right to know when you&amp;rsquo;ve been hacked&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That&amp;rsquo;s because the laws governing when companies have to inform customers about data breaches vary widely around the country, prompting &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.marketwatch.com/story/you-may-soon-have-the-right-to-know-when-youve-been-hacked-2017-03-15&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.marketwatch.com/story/you-may-soon-have-the-right-to-know-when-youve-been-hacked-2017-03-15&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Webroot Drives Twelfth Consecutive Quarter of Double-Digit Business Growth&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Finance MSP administrators can use Unity to securely integrate services and data sets to Webroot SecureAnywhere Business Endpoint Protection.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/webroot-drives-twelfth-consecutive-quarter-140000014.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/webroot-drives-twelfth-consecutive-quarter-140000014.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
